Subject: Re: [VB] Easier ball Joint Replacement?

There was one made years ago called a "Time pirate" that allowed you to
remove and install ball joints while on the vehicle itself. Not hydraulic,
but required a big impact gun to do it. One of those "cool tools" for sure.

